" remapping Escape
nnoremap jk <esc>
" Remap in Normal mode
inoremap jk <esc>
" Remap in Insert and Replace mode
vnoremap jk <esc>
" Remap in Visual and Select mode
xnoremap jk <esc>
" Remap in Visual mode
snoremap jk <esc>
" Remap in Select mode
cnoremap jk <C-C>
" Remap in Command-line mode
onoremap jk <esc>
" Remap in Operator pending mode

